===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# Either of two species of [[bird]] in the family ''[[Meleagrididae]]'' with fan-shaped [[tail]]s and [[wattle]]d [[neck]]s.
# (''colloquial'') A failure.
#:''That film was a '''turkey'''.''
# (''slang, usually derogatory'') A stupid or incompetent person.
#:''The '''turkey''' cut in front of me and then berated me for running into him.''
# {{context|Bowling}}: The act of throwing three strikes in a row.

